{% comment %}
============================================================
セクション名: 安心保証バナー
用途: 30 日保証・返金保証・初期不良対応などの保証内容を視覚的に提示し、購入前の不安を取り除くためのバナー
推奨設置場所: 商品ページの購入ボタン直下、トップページのファーストビュー直後、LP のクロージング前
カスタマイズポイント:
  - セクション見出し・サブコピー
  - 保証項目ブロック(アイコン・タイトル・本文)の追加・編集
  - 背景色・アクセントカラー・文字色
  - レイアウト(カードグリッド型)
  - PC の列数・スマホでの表示方法
注意点:
  - アイコン画像は正方形(推奨 200 × 200px、PNG 透過)を用意することを推奨
  - ブロック数は 3〜4 個が最も見栄えがよい
  - 画像未設定時はアイコン部分が非表示になる
動作確認バージョン: Online Store 2.0
ライセンス: ALSEL Original
============================================================
{% endcomment %}

{%- assign sec_heading = section.settings.heading | escape -%}
{%- assign mobile_layout = section.settings.mobile_layout -%}

<section class="alsel-assurance-badge alsel-assurance-badge--mobile-{{ mobile_layout }}" aria-label="{{ sec_heading }}" style="background: {{ section.settings.bg_color }};">
  <div class="alsel-assurance-badge__inner">
    {%- if section.settings.heading != blank -%}
      <h2 class="alsel-assurance-badge__heading" style="color: {{ section.settings.text_color }};">
        {{ section.settings.heading }}
      </h2>
    {%- endif -%}
    {%- if section.settings.subheading != blank -%}
      <p class="alsel-assurance-badge__sub" style="color: {{ section.settings.text_color }};">
        {{ section.settings.subheading }}
      </p>
    {%- endif -%}

    {%- if section.blocks.size == 0 -%}
      <p class="alsel-assurance-badge__empty">
        現在表示できる保証項目はありません。テーマエディタからブロックを追加してください。
      </p>
    {%- else -%}
      <div class="alsel-assurance-badge__grid">
        {%- for block in section.blocks -%}
          {%- assign block_title = block.settings.title | escape -%}
          <article class="alsel-assurance-badge__card" {{ block.shopify_attributes }}>
            <div class="alsel-assurance-badge__icon-wrap" style="background: {{ section.settings.accent_color }}1a;">
              {%- if block.settings.icon != blank -%}
                {{ block.settings.icon
                  | image_url: width: 200
                  | image_tag: loading: 'lazy', class: 'alsel-assurance-badge__icon', alt: block_title, widths: '100, 150, 200' }}
              {%- else -%}
                <svg class="alsel-assurance-badge__icon-default" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="{{ section.settings.accent_color }}" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
                  <path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/>
                  <polyline points="9 12 11 14 15 10"/>
                </svg>
              {%- endif -%}
            </div>
            {%- if block.settings.title != blank -%}
              <h3 class="alsel-assurance-badge__title">{{ block.settings.title }}</h3>
            {%- endif -%}
            {%- if block.settings.body != blank -%}
              <p class="alsel-assurance-badge__body">{{ block.settings.body }}</p>
            {%- endif -%}
          </article>
        {%- endfor -%}
      </div>
    {%- endif -%}
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .alsel-assurance-badge { padding: 3rem 1rem; }
  .alsel-assurance-badge__inner { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .alsel-assurance-badge__heading { font-size: clamp(1.4rem, 4vw, 2.2rem); font-weight: 700; text-align: center; margin: 0 0 0.75rem; line-height: 1.4; }
  .alsel-assurance-badge__sub { font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.7; text-align: center; margin: 0 0 2.5rem; opacity: 0.85; }
  .alsel-assurance-badge__empty { text-align: center; color: #888; padding: 2rem 0; }

  /* モバイル: 1列表示(デフォルト) */
  .alsel-assurance-badge__grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 1.25rem; }

  /* モバイル: 2列表示 */
  .alsel-assurance-badge--mobile-two .alsel-assurance-badge__grid {
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 0.85rem;
  }

  /* モバイル: 横スワイプ */
  .alsel-assurance-badge--mobile-swipe .alsel-assurance-badge__grid {
    display: flex;
    grid-template-columns: none;
    overflow-x: auto;
    scroll-snap-type: x mandatory;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding-bottom: 0.75rem;
    -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;
  }
  .alsel-assurance-badge--mobile-swipe .alsel-assurance-badge__card {
    flex: 0 0 80%;
    scroll-snap-align: start;
  }

  .alsel-assurance-badge__card {
    background: #ffffff;
    border-radius: 14px;
    padding: 1.75rem 1.25rem;
    text-align: center;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 14px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.06);
    border: 1px solid rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.04);
    transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
    scroll-snap-align: start;
  }
  .alsel-assurance-badge__card:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.1); }
  .alsel-assurance-badge__icon-wrap {
    width: 72px; height: 72px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    margin: 0 auto 1rem;
  }
  .alsel-assurance-badge__icon { width: 44px; height: 44px; object-fit: contain; }
  .alsel-assurance-badge__icon-default { width: 36px; height: 36px; }
  .alsel-assurance-badge__title { font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; margin: 0 0 0.6rem; color: #0f172a; line-height: 1.4; }
  .alsel-assurance-badge__body { font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.7; color: #475569; margin: 0; }

  @media (min-width: 750px) {
    .alsel-assurance-badge { padding: 5rem 2rem; }
    .alsel-assurance-badge__grid,
    .alsel-assurance-badge--mobile-two .alsel-assurance-badge__grid,
    .alsel-assurance-badge--mobile-swipe .alsel-assurance-badge__grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat({{ section.settings.columns_pc }}, 1fr);
      gap: 1.75rem;
      overflow: visible;
      padding-bottom: 0;
    }
    .alsel-assurance-badge--mobile-swipe .alsel-assurance-badge__card {
      flex: initial;
    }
    .alsel-assurance-badge__card { padding: 2.25rem 1.5rem; }
    .alsel-assurance-badge__icon-wrap { width: 84px; height: 84px; }
    .alsel-assurance-badge__icon { width: 52px; height: 52px; }
    .alsel-assurance-badge__icon-default { width: 42px; height: 42px; }
  }
</style>

