{% comment %}
============================================================
セクション名: 法人向け問い合わせCTA
用途: 大口注文・卸販売・見積もりなど、法人顧客からの問い合わせを促すための専用 CTA。BtoB 取引や OEM、ノベルティ用途など、通常の購入フローとは別ルートで連絡してほしい場合に使う
推奨設置場所: トップページの下部、商品ページの下部、固定ページ(会社案内・卸販売案内)
カスタマイズポイント:
  - 見出し・サブコピー・補足説明
  - 訴求ポイント(3 つまで、アイコン + テキスト)
  - メインボタン(問い合わせフォーム誘導)
  - サブボタン(電話・メール誘導)
  - 背景色・文字色・アクセントカラー
  - レイアウト(中央寄せ / 左右 2 カラム)
注意点:
  - メインボタンのリンク先には、問い合わせフォームまたは法人専用ページの URL を設定する
  - 電話番号は tel: スキーマで自動リンク化される
  - アイコンは絵文字または短いテキストで指定(画像不要)
動作確認バージョン: Online Store 2.0
ライセンス: ALSEL Original
============================================================
{% endcomment %}

{%- assign aria_label = section.settings.heading | default: '法人向け問い合わせ' | escape -%}

<section class="alsel-b2b-inquiry-cta alsel-b2b-inquiry-cta--{{ section.settings.layout }}" aria-label="{{ aria_label }}">
  <div class="alsel-b2b-inquiry-cta__inner">
    <div class="alsel-b2b-inquiry-cta__lead">
      {%- if section.settings.badge != blank -%}
        <span class="alsel-b2b-inquiry-cta__badge">{{ section.settings.badge }}</span>
      {%- endif -%}
      {%- if section.settings.heading != blank -%}
        <h2 class="alsel-b2b-inquiry-cta__heading">{{ section.settings.heading }}</h2>
      {%- endif -%}
      {%- if section.settings.subheading != blank -%}
        <p class="alsel-b2b-inquiry-cta__sub">{{ section.settings.subheading }}</p>
      {%- endif -%}
      {%- if section.settings.description != blank -%}
        <div class="alsel-b2b-inquiry-cta__desc">{{ section.settings.description }}</div>
      {%- endif -%}
    </div>

    <div class="alsel-b2b-inquiry-cta__body">
      {%- if section.blocks.size > 0 -%}
        <ul class="alsel-b2b-inquiry-cta__points">
          {%- for block in section.blocks -%}
            <li class="alsel-b2b-inquiry-cta__point" {{ block.shopify_attributes }}>
              {%- if block.settings.icon != blank -%}
                <span class="alsel-b2b-inquiry-cta__icon" aria-hidden="true">{{ block.settings.icon }}</span>
              {%- endif -%}
              <div class="alsel-b2b-inquiry-cta__point-text">
                {%- if block.settings.title != blank -%}
                  <p class="alsel-b2b-inquiry-cta__point-title">{{ block.settings.title }}</p>
                {%- endif -%}
                {%- if block.settings.body != blank -%}
                  <p class="alsel-b2b-inquiry-cta__point-body">{{ block.settings.body }}</p>
                {%- endif -%}
              </div>
            </li>
          {%- endfor -%}
        </ul>
      {%- endif -%}

      <div class="alsel-b2b-inquiry-cta__actions">
        {%- if section.settings.primary_text != blank and section.settings.primary_link != blank -%}
          <a class="alsel-b2b-inquiry-cta__primary" href="{{ section.settings.primary_link }}" aria-label="{{ section.settings.primary_text | escape }}">
            {{ section.settings.primary_text }}
            <span class="alsel-b2b-inquiry-cta__arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span>
          </a>
        {%- endif -%}
        <div class="alsel-b2b-inquiry-cta__sub-actions">
          {%- if section.settings.tel_number != blank -%}
            {%- assign tel_clean = section.settings.tel_number | replace: '-', '' | replace: ' ', '' -%}
            <a class="alsel-b2b-inquiry-cta__tel" href="tel:{{ tel_clean }}" aria-label="電話で問い合わせ {{ section.settings.tel_number | escape }}">
              <span class="alsel-b2b-inquiry-cta__tel-icon" aria-hidden="true">☎</span>
              <span class="alsel-b2b-inquiry-cta__tel-text">
                <span class="alsel-b2b-inquiry-cta__tel-label">{{ section.settings.tel_label }}</span>
                <span class="alsel-b2b-inquiry-cta__tel-number">{{ section.settings.tel_number }}</span>
                {%- if section.settings.tel_hours != blank -%}
                  <span class="alsel-b2b-inquiry-cta__tel-hours">{{ section.settings.tel_hours }}</span>
                {%- endif -%}
              </span>
            </a>
          {%- endif -%}
          {%- if section.settings.mail_address != blank -%}
            <a class="alsel-b2b-inquiry-cta__mail" href="mailto:{{ section.settings.mail_address }}" aria-label="メールで問い合わせ">
              <span class="alsel-b2b-inquiry-cta__mail-icon" aria-hidden="true">✉</span>
              <span class="alsel-b2b-inquiry-cta__mail-text">{{ section.settings.mail_address }}</span>
            </a>
          {%- endif -%}
        </div>
        {%- if section.settings.note != blank -%}
          <p class="alsel-b2b-inquiry-cta__note">{{ section.settings.note }}</p>
        {%- endif -%}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
