セクション名: 縦長漫画風セクション
用途: 悩み→解決→商品紹介の流れを漫画のコマ風に見せて、訴求力を高めるLPパーツ
推奨設置場所: 商品LPの中盤、お客様の声の前、商品ページのカスタムLP内
カスタマイズポイント:
  - セクション全体の見出し・サブコピー
  - 各コマ(ブロック)の画像・セリフ・キャラ名・コマタイプ(悩み/解決/紹介)
  - 背景色・コマの枠線色・吹き出し色
  - 最下部のCTAボタン(文字・リンク・色)
注意点:
  - コマ画像は推奨 800 × 600px、JPEG または PNG
  - ブロックは 3〜6 コマ推奨。順番に「悩み → 気づき → 解決 → 紹介」と並べると効果的です
  - 漫画風の縦長レイアウトのため、スマホ最適化が前提
動作確認バージョン: Online Store 2.0
ライセンス: ALSEL Original
============================================================
{% endcomment %}

{%- assign heading_alt = section.settings.heading | escape -%}

<section class="alsel-comic-story-section" aria-label="{{ heading_alt }}">
  <div class="alsel-comic-story-section__header">
    {%- if section.settings.badge_text != blank -%}
      <span class="alsel-comic-story-section__badge">{{ section.settings.badge_text }}</span>
    {%- endif -%}
    {%- if section.settings.heading != blank -%}
      <h2 class="alsel-comic-story-section__heading">{{ section.settings.heading }}</h2>
    {%- endif -%}
    {%- if section.settings.subheading != blank -%}
      <p class="alsel-comic-story-section__sub">{{ section.settings.subheading }}</p>
    {%- endif -%}
  </div>

  <div class="alsel-comic-story-section__panels">
    {%- if section.blocks.size == 0 -%}
      <p class="alsel-comic-story-section__empty" style="text-align:center;color:#888;padding:2rem 0;">
        コマはまだ登録されていません。テーマエディタからブロックを追加してください。
      </p>
    {%- endif -%}

    {%- for block in section.blocks -%}
      {%- assign panel_alt = block.settings.character_name | append: ' のコマ' | escape -%}
      <article class="alsel-comic-story-section__panel alsel-comic-story-section__panel--{{ block.settings.panel_type }}" {{ block.shopify_attributes }}>
        <div class="alsel-comic-story-section__panel-number">
          <span>{{ forloop.index }}</span>
        </div>

        {%- if block.settings.panel_type != 'none' -%}
          <span class="alsel-comic-story-section__panel-tag">
            {%- case block.settings.panel_type -%}
              {%- when 'problem' -%}お悩み
              {%- when 'discover' -%}発見
              {%- when 'solution' -%}解決
              {%- when 'product' -%}商品紹介
            {%- endcase -%}
          </span>
        {%- endif -%}

        <div class="alsel-comic-story-section__panel-inner">
          {%- if block.settings.image != blank -%}
            <div class="alsel-comic-story-section__panel-media">
              {{ block.settings.image | image_url: width: 800 | image_tag: loading: 'lazy', class: 'alsel-comic-story-section__panel-image', alt: panel_alt, widths: '375, 600, 800' }}
            </div>
          {%- endif -%}

          <div class="alsel-comic-story-section__panel-text">
            {%- if block.settings.balloon_text != blank -%}
              <div class="alsel-comic-story-section__balloon">
                <p class="alsel-comic-story-section__balloon-text">{{ block.settings.balloon_text }}</p>
              </div>
            {%- endif -%}
            {%- if block.settings.character_name != blank -%}
              <p class="alsel-comic-story-section__character">{{ block.settings.character_name }}</p>
            {%- endif -%}
          </div>
        </div>

        {%- unless forloop.last -%}
          <div class="alsel-comic-story-section__arrow" aria-hidden="true">▼</div>
        {%- endunless -%}
      </article>
    {%- endfor -%}
  </div>

  {%- if section.settings.cta_text != blank and section.settings.cta_link != blank -%}
    <div class="alsel-comic-story-section__cta-wrap">
      {%- if section.settings.cta_lead != blank -%}
        <p class="alsel-comic-story-section__cta-lead">{{ section.settings.cta_lead }}</p>
      {%- endif -%}
      <a class="alsel-comic-story-section__cta" href="{{ section.settings.cta_link }}" aria-label="{{ section.settings.cta_text | escape }}">
        {{ section.settings.cta_text }}
      </a>
    </div>
  {%- endif -%}
</section>

