{% comment %}
============================================================
セクション名: 在庫残りわずか表示
用途: 商品ページや LP で「残りわずか」「在庫◯個」など希少性を訴求し、購入を後押しする
推奨設置場所: 商品ページの購入ボタン付近、LP の CTA 直前
カスタマイズポイント:
  - 見出し・メッセージ文・在庫数の数値
  - バッジの色(背景色・文字色)
  - 警告アイコンの表示有無
  - 在庫プログレスバーの表示有無と総数
  - アニメーション(点滅)の有無
注意点:
  - 在庫数はテーマエディタから手動入力する数値である(Shopify の実在庫とは連動しない)
  - 実在庫連動は別途カスタム開発が必要
  - 過度な訴求は景品表示法に抵触する恐れがあるため、虚偽の在庫数は記載しないこと
動作確認バージョン: Online Store 2.0
ライセンス: ALSEL Original
============================================================
{% endcomment %}

{%- assign stock_now = section.settings.stock_count | times: 1 -%}
{%- assign stock_total = section.settings.stock_total | times: 1 -%}
{%- if stock_total > 0 -%}
  {%- assign stock_percent = stock_now | times: 100.0 | divided_by: stock_total -%}
{%- else -%}
  {%- assign stock_percent = 0 -%}
{%- endif -%}

<section class="alsel-low-stock-badge" aria-label="{{ section.settings.heading | escape }}">
  <div class="alsel-low-stock-badge__inner">
    <div class="alsel-low-stock-badge__badge{%- if section.settings.blink %} alsel-low-stock-badge__badge--blink{%- endif -%}">
      {%- if section.settings.show_icon -%}
        <span class="alsel-low-stock-badge__icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20">
            <path d="M12 2L1 21h22L12 2zm0 6l7.5 13h-15L12 8zm-1 4v4h2v-4h-2zm0 5v2h2v-2h-2z" fill="currentColor"/>
          </svg>
        </span>
      {%- endif -%}
      <span class="alsel-low-stock-badge__label">{{ section.settings.badge_text }}</span>
    </div>

    {%- if section.settings.heading != blank -%}
      <h2 class="alsel-low-stock-badge__heading">{{ section.settings.heading }}</h2>
    {%- endif -%}

    {%- if section.settings.show_count -%}
      <p class="alsel-low-stock-badge__count">
        {{ section.settings.count_prefix }}
        <span class="alsel-low-stock-badge__number">{{ stock_now }}</span>
        <span class="alsel-low-stock-badge__unit">{{ section.settings.count_unit }}</span>
      </p>
    {%- endif -%}

    {%- if section.settings.show_bar and stock_total > 0 -%}
      <div class="alsel-low-stock-badge__bar" role="progressbar" aria-valuenow="{{ stock_now }}" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="{{ stock_total }}">
        <div class="alsel-low-stock-badge__bar-fill" style="width: {{ stock_percent }}%;"></div>
      </div>
      <p class="alsel-low-stock-badge__bar-text">
        全 {{ stock_total }} {{ section.settings.count_unit }}のうち、残り <strong>{{ stock_now }}</strong> {{ section.settings.count_unit }}です。
      </p>
    {%- endif -%}

    {%- if section.settings.message != blank -%}
      <p class="alsel-low-stock-badge__message">{{ section.settings.message }}</p>
    {%- endif -%}

    {%- if section.settings.cta_text != blank and section.settings.cta_link != blank -%}
      <a class="alsel-low-stock-badge__cta" href="{{ section.settings.cta_link }}">
        {{ section.settings.cta_text }}
      </a>
    {%- endif -%}
  </div>
</section>

