{% comment %}
============================================================
セクション名: 価格帯別おすすめ
用途: 予算別に商品を提案し、お客様の購入検討をスムーズにするためのセクション。3,000 円以下・5,000 円以下・1 万円以下など、価格帯ごとに商品をまとめて訴求する
推奨設置場所: トップページ・コレクションページ・ギフト特集 LP の中盤
カスタマイズポイント:
  - セクション見出し・サブコピー
  - 各価格帯カード(タイトル・価格表示・キャッチ・画像・リンク先)
  - カード背景色・文字色・ボタン色
  - 全体の背景色
注意点:
  - カード画像は推奨 800 × 600px、JPEG または PNG
  - ブロックは 2〜4 個推奨。それ以外の数は CSS で grid 調整が必要
  - リンク先にはコレクションページ(/collections/under-3000 など)を指定するのがおすすめ
動作確認バージョン: Online Store 2.0
ライセンス: ALSEL Original
============================================================
{% endcomment %}

<section class="alsel-price-range-guide" aria-label="{{ section.settings.heading | escape }}">
  <div class="alsel-price-range-guide__head">
    {%- if section.settings.heading != blank -%}
      <h2 class="alsel-price-range-guide__heading">{{ section.settings.heading }}</h2>
    {%- endif -%}
    {%- if section.settings.subheading != blank -%}
      <p class="alsel-price-range-guide__sub">{{ section.settings.subheading }}</p>
    {%- endif -%}
  </div>

  {%- if section.blocks.size == 0 -%}
    <p class="alsel-price-range-guide__empty">
      表示する価格帯はまだ登録されていません。テーマエディタからブロックを追加してください。
    </p>
  {%- endif -%}

  <div class="alsel-price-range-guide__grid">
    {%- for block in section.blocks -%}
      {%- assign card_alt = block.settings.title | escape -%}
      <article class="alsel-price-range-guide__card" {{ block.shopify_attributes }} style="background:{{ block.settings.card_bg }};color:{{ block.settings.card_color }};">
        <div class="alsel-price-range-guide__media">
          {%- if block.settings.image != blank -%}
            {{ block.settings.image
              | image_url: width: 800
              | image_tag: loading: 'lazy', class: 'alsel-price-range-guide__img', alt: card_alt, widths: '375, 600, 800' }}
          {%- else -%}
            <div class="alsel-price-range-guide__placeholder" aria-hidden="true"></div>
          {%- endif -%}
          {%- if block.settings.badge != blank -%}
            <span class="alsel-price-range-guide__badge">{{ block.settings.badge }}</span>
          {%- endif -%}
        </div>
        <div class="alsel-price-range-guide__body">
          {%- if block.settings.price_label != blank -%}
            <p class="alsel-price-range-guide__price">{{ block.settings.price_label }}</p>
          {%- endif -%}
          {%- if block.settings.title != blank -%}
            <h3 class="alsel-price-range-guide__title">{{ block.settings.title }}</h3>
          {%- endif -%}
          {%- if block.settings.description != blank -%}
            <p class="alsel-price-range-guide__desc">{{ block.settings.description }}</p>
          {%- endif -%}
          {%- if block.settings.button_text != blank and block.settings.button_link != blank -%}
            <a class="alsel-price-range-guide__cta" href="{{ block.settings.button_link }}" style="background:{{ block.settings.button_bg }};color:{{ block.settings.button_color }};" aria-label="{{ block.settings.title | escape }}の商品一覧を見る">
              {{ block.settings.button_text }}
              <span class="alsel-price-range-guide__arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span>
            </a>
          {%- endif -%}
        </div>
      </article>
    {%- endfor -%}
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .alsel-price-range-guide { padding: 3rem 1rem; background: {{ section.settings.bg_color }}; }
  .alsel-price-range-guide__head { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto 2rem; text-align: center; }
  .alsel-price-range-guide__heading { font-size: clamp(1.4rem, 4vw, 2.2rem); font-weight: 700; margin: 0 0 0.75rem; color: {{ section.settings.text_color }}; }
  .alsel-price-range-guide__sub { font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.7; margin: 0; color: {{ section.settings.text_color }}; opacity: 0.8; }
  .alsel-price-range-guide__empty { text-align: center; color: #888; padding: 2rem 0; margin: 0; }
  .alsel-price-range-guide__grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 1.5rem; max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .alsel-price-range-guide__card { border-radius: 14px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 4px 14px rgba(0,0,0,0.07); display: flex; flex-direction: column; transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease; }
  .alsel-price-range-guide__card:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
  .alsel-price-range-guide__media { position: relative; aspect-ratio: 4 / 3; overflow: hidden; background: #f1f5f9; }
  .alsel-price-range-guide__img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; display: block; }
  .alsel-price-range-guide__placeholder { width: 100%; height: 100%; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e2e8f0 0%, #cbd5e1 100%); }
  .alsel-price-range-guide__badge { position: absolute; top: 12px; left: 12px; background: #ef4444; color: #fff; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 700; padding: 0.3rem 0.7rem; border-radius: 9999px; }
  .alsel-price-range-guide__body { padding: 1.5rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.6rem; flex: 1; }
  .alsel-price-range-guide__price { font-size: 1.4rem; font-weight: 700; margin: 0; letter-spacing: 0.02em; }
  .alsel-price-range-guide__title { font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; margin: 0; line-height: 1.4; }
  .alsel-price-range-guide__desc { font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.7; margin: 0; opacity: 0.85; flex: 1; }
  .alsel-price-range-guide__cta { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 0.4rem; margin-top: 0.5rem; padding: 0.8rem 1.4rem; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 9999px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 0.95rem; text-align: center; transition: opacity 0.2s ease; }
  .alsel-price-range-guide__cta:hover { opacity: 0.85; }
  .alsel-price-range-guide__arrow { transition: transform 0.2s ease; }
  .alsel-price-range-guide__cta:hover .alsel-price-range-guide__arrow { transform: translateX(3px); }
  @media (min-width: 750px) {
    .alsel-price-range-guide { padding: 5rem 2rem; }
    .alsel-price-range-guide__grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 2rem; }
  }
</style>

