{% comment %}
============================================================
セクション名: 生産者紹介
用途: 農産品・食品・工芸品・D2C ブランドで、作り手の顔と想いを伝える定番セクション。商品の背景にあるストーリーを訴求し、購入の納得感を高めるために使う。
推奨設置場所: トップページの中盤、商品ページの下部、ブランドストーリーページ(LP)
カスタマイズポイント:
  - 生産者の顔写真(円形 / 角丸 / 四角を選択可能)
  - 名前・肩書き(○○農園 代表 など)
  - 産地・所在地の表示
  - 紹介文(長文に対応)
  - こだわりポイント(ブロックで自由に追加)
  - 詳細ページへのリンクボタン
  - レイアウト(写真の位置: 左 / 右)
  - 背景色・文字色
注意点:
  - 顔写真は推奨 800 × 800px(正方形、JPEG または PNG)
  - こだわりポイントは 2〜4 個を推奨
  - Online Store 2.0 必須
動作確認バージョン: Online Store 2.0
ライセンス: ALSEL Original
============================================================
{% endcomment %}

<section class="alsel-producer-profile alsel-producer-profile--{{ section.settings.layout }}" aria-label="生産者紹介: {{ section.settings.producer_name | escape }}">
  <div class="alsel-producer-profile__inner">
    {%- if section.settings.eyebrow != blank -%}
      <p class="alsel-producer-profile__eyebrow">{{ section.settings.eyebrow }}</p>
    {%- endif -%}
    {%- if section.settings.heading != blank -%}
      <h2 class="alsel-producer-profile__heading">{{ section.settings.heading }}</h2>
    {%- endif -%}

    <div class="alsel-producer-profile__grid">
      <div class="alsel-producer-profile__media">
        {%- if section.settings.photo != blank -%}
          {%- assign alt_1 = section.settings.producer_name | escape -%}
{{ section.settings.photo
            | image_url: width: 800
            | image_tag:
              loading: 'lazy',
              class: 'alsel-producer-profile__photo',
              alt: alt_1,
              widths: '300, 500, 700, 800',
              sizes: '(min-width: 750px) 40vw, 80vw' }}
        {%- else -%}
          <div class="alsel-producer-profile__photo alsel-producer-profile__photo--placeholder" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        {%- endif -%}
        {%- if section.settings.location != blank -%}
          <p class="alsel-producer-profile__location">
            <span class="alsel-producer-profile__pin" aria-hidden="true">📍</span>
            {{ section.settings.location | escape }}
          </p>
        {%- endif -%}
      </div>

      <div class="alsel-producer-profile__body">
        {%- if section.settings.producer_name != blank -%}
          <p class="alsel-producer-profile__role">{{ section.settings.role | escape }}</p>
          <h3 class="alsel-producer-profile__name">{{ section.settings.producer_name | escape }}</h3>
        {%- endif -%}

        {%- if section.settings.description != blank -%}
          <div class="alsel-producer-profile__description">{{ section.settings.description }}</div>
        {%- endif -%}

        {%- if section.blocks.size > 0 -%}
          <ul class="alsel-producer-profile__points">
            {%- for block in section.blocks -%}
              {%- if block.type == 'point' -%}
                <li class="alsel-producer-profile__point" {{ block.shopify_attributes }}>
                  {%- if block.settings.icon != blank -%}
                    <span class="alsel-producer-profile__point-icon" aria-hidden="true">{{ block.settings.icon }}</span>
                  {%- endif -%}
                  <div class="alsel-producer-profile__point-text">
                    <strong class="alsel-producer-profile__point-title">{{ block.settings.title | escape }}</strong>
                    {%- if block.settings.body != blank -%}
                      <span class="alsel-producer-profile__point-body">{{ block.settings.body | escape }}</span>
                    {%- endif -%}
                  </div>
                </li>
              {%- endif -%}
            {%- endfor -%}
          </ul>
        {%- endif -%}

        {%- if section.settings.cta_text != blank and section.settings.cta_link != blank -%}
          <a class="alsel-producer-profile__cta" href="{{ section.settings.cta_link }}" aria-label="{{ section.settings.cta_text | escape }}">
            {{ section.settings.cta_text | escape }}
            <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
          </a>
        {%- endif -%}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
