{% comment %}
============================================================
セクション名: 商品動画ギャラリー(タブ切替)
用途: 商品紹介・使い方・お客様の声などの複数動画を、タブで切り替えて見せるためのギャラリーセクション
推奨設置場所: 商品ページ・トップページ・LP の中盤(商品の魅力を動画で伝えたい場面)
カスタマイズポイント:
  - セクション見出し・サブコピー
  - 各動画のタブ名・サムネイル画像・動画 URL(YouTube / Vimeo / MP4)
  - 動画の説明文
  - 背景色・アクセントカラー
  - ブロックの追加・削除でタブ数を変更
注意点:
  - サムネイル画像は推奨 1280 × 720px(16:9)、JPEG または PNG
  - 動画 URL は YouTube の埋め込み URL(https://www.youtube.com/embed/xxxxx)を推奨
  - MP4 直接配信の場合は Shopify Files にアップロードした URL を指定
  - ブロックは 2〜6 個推奨。1 個でも動作するがタブとしての意味が薄れる
動作確認バージョン: Online Store 2.0
ライセンス: ALSEL Original
============================================================
{% endcomment %}

<section class="alsel-product-video-gallery" aria-label="{{ section.settings.heading | escape }}">
  <div class="alsel-product-video-gallery__inner">
    {%- if section.settings.heading != blank -%}
      <h2 class="alsel-product-video-gallery__heading">{{ section.settings.heading }}</h2>
    {%- endif -%}
    {%- if section.settings.subheading != blank -%}
      <p class="alsel-product-video-gallery__sub">{{ section.settings.subheading }}</p>
    {%- endif -%}

    {%- if section.blocks.size == 0 -%}
      <p class="alsel-product-video-gallery__empty">
        動画はまだ登録されていません。テーマエディタからブロックを追加してください。
      </p>
    {%- else -%}
      <div class="alsel-product-video-gallery__tabs" role="tablist">
        {%- for block in section.blocks -%}
          {%- assign tab_alt = block.settings.tab_label | escape -%}
          <button
            class="alsel-product-video-gallery__tab{%- if forloop.first %} is-active{%- endif -%}"
            role="tab"
            type="button"
            data-target="alsel-pvg-panel-{{ section.id }}-{{ forloop.index }}"
            aria-selected="{%- if forloop.first -%}true{%- else -%}false{%- endif -%}"
            {{ block.shopify_attributes }}
          >
            {%- if block.settings.thumbnail != blank -%}
              {{ block.settings.thumbnail | image_url: width: 320 | image_tag: loading: 'lazy', class: 'alsel-product-video-gallery__tab-thumb', alt: tab_alt, widths: '160, 320, 480' }}
            {%- endif -%}
            <span class="alsel-product-video-gallery__tab-label">{{ block.settings.tab_label }}</span>
          </button>
        {%- endfor -%}
      </div>

      <div class="alsel-product-video-gallery__panels">
        {%- for block in section.blocks -%}
          <div
            class="alsel-product-video-gallery__panel{%- if forloop.first %} is-active{%- endif -%}"
            id="alsel-pvg-panel-{{ section.id }}-{{ forloop.index }}"
            role="tabpanel"
          >
            <div class="alsel-product-video-gallery__video">
              {%- assign video_url = block.settings.video_url -%}
              {%- if video_url contains 'youtube.com' or video_url contains 'youtu.be' or video_url contains 'vimeo.com' -%}
                <iframe
                  src="{{ video_url }}"
                  title="{{ block.settings.tab_label | escape }}"
                  loading="lazy"
                  allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture"
                  allowfullscreen
                ></iframe>
              {%- elsif video_url != blank -%}
                <video controls preload="metadata" playsinline>
                  <source src="{{ video_url }}" type="video/mp4">
                </video>
              {%- elsif block.settings.thumbnail != blank -%}
                {%- assign fallback_alt = block.settings.tab_label | escape -%}
                {{ block.settings.thumbnail | image_url: width: 1280 | image_tag: loading: 'lazy', class: 'alsel-product-video-gallery__fallback', alt: fallback_alt, widths: '640, 960, 1280' }}
              {%- else -%}
                <div class="alsel-product-video-gallery__placeholder">
                  動画 URL を設定してください。
                </div>
              {%- endif -%}
            </div>
            {%- if block.settings.video_title != blank -%}
              <h3 class="alsel-product-video-gallery__video-title">{{ block.settings.video_title }}</h3>
            {%- endif -%}
            {%- if block.settings.video_body != blank -%}
              <p class="alsel-product-video-gallery__video-body">{{ block.settings.video_body }}</p>
            {%- endif -%}
          </div>
        {%- endfor -%}
      </div>
    {%- endif -%}
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .alsel-product-video-gallery { padding: 3rem 1rem; background: {{ section.settings.bg_color }}; }
  .alsel-product-video-gallery__inner { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .alsel-product-video-gallery__heading { font-size: clamp(1.4rem, 4vw, 2.2rem); text-align: center; margin: 0 0 0.75rem; color: {{ section.settings.text_color }}; font-weight: 700; }
  .alsel-product-video-gallery__sub { text-align: center; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.7; color: {{ section.settings.text_color }}; opacity: 0.8; margin: 0 0 2rem; }
  .alsel-product-video-gallery__empty { text-align: center; color: #888; padding: 2rem 0; }

  .alsel-product-video-gallery__tabs { display: flex; flex-wrap: nowrap; gap: 0.75rem; overflow-x: auto; padding: 0.5rem 0 1rem; margin: 0 0 1.5rem; scrollbar-width: thin; }
  .alsel-product-video-gallery__tab { flex: 0 0 auto; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; padding: 0.5rem; background: #fff; border: 2px solid transparent; border-radius: 10px; cursor: pointer; transition: border-color 0.2s, transform 0.2s; min-width: 120px; }
  .alsel-product-video-gallery__tab:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); }
  .alsel-product-video-gallery__tab.is-active { border-color: {{ section.settings.accent_color }}; }
  .alsel-product-video-gallery__tab-thumb { width: 100%; aspect-ratio: 16 / 9; object-fit: cover; border-radius: 6px; display: block; }
  .alsel-product-video-gallery__tab-label { font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 700; color: {{ section.settings.text_color }}; text-align: center; line-height: 1.4; }

  .alsel-product-video-gallery__panel { display: none; }
  .alsel-product-video-gallery__panel.is-active { display: block; animation: alsel-pvg-fade 0.3s ease; }
  @keyframes alsel-pvg-fade { from { opacity: 0; } to { opacity: 1; } }

  .alsel-product-video-gallery__video { position: relative; width: 100%; aspect-ratio: 16 / 9; background: #000; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
  .alsel-product-video-gallery__video iframe,
  .alsel-product-video-gallery__video video,
  .alsel-product-video-gallery__fallback { position: absolute; inset: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; border: 0; object-fit: cover; }
  .alsel-product-video-gallery__placeholder { position: absolute; inset: 0; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; color: #fff; font-size: 0.95rem; }

  .alsel-product-video-gallery__video-title { font-size: 1.15rem; font-weight: 700; margin: 1.25rem 0 0.5rem; color: {{ section.settings.text_color }}; }
  .alsel-product-video-gallery__video-body { font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.7; color: {{ section.settings.text_color }}; opacity: 0.85; margin: 0; }

  @media (min-width: 750px) {
    .alsel-product-video-gallery { padding: 5rem 2rem; }
    .alsel-product-video-gallery__tabs { flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center; }
    .alsel-product-video-gallery__tab { min-width: 160px; }
  }
</style>

<script>
  (function() {
    var root = document.currentScript.previousElementSibling;
    while (root && !root.classList.contains('alsel-product-video-gallery')) {
      root = root.previousElementSibling;
    }
    if (!root) return;
    var tabs = root.querySelectorAll('.alsel-product-video-gallery__tab');
    var panels = root.querySelectorAll('.alsel-product-video-gallery__panel');
    tabs.forEach(function(tab) {
      tab.addEventListener('click', function() {
        var target = tab.getAttribute('data-target');
        tabs.forEach(function(t) { t.classList.remove('is-active'); t.setAttribute('aria-selected', 'false'); });
        panels.forEach(function(p) { p.classList.remove('is-active'); });
        tab.classList.add('is-active');
        tab.setAttribute('aria-selected', 'true');
        var panel = root.querySelector('#' + target);
        if (panel) panel.classList.add('is-active');
      });
    });
  })();
</script>

