{% comment %}
============================================================
セクション名: 関連商品スライダー
用途: 商品ページの下部に「あわせて買いたい商品」や「おすすめ商品」を横スクロールで表示し、回遊率を高めるためのセクション
推奨設置場所: 商品ページ(product.json)の下部、もしくはトップページのおすすめ枠
カスタマイズポイント:
  - 表示する商品リスト(コレクションを選択)
  - セクション見出し・サブコピー
  - 表示件数(最大 12 件)
  - カードの角丸・背景色・ボタン色
  - 価格・SOLD OUT 表示の ON/OFF
注意点:
  - コレクション未選択時はガイドメッセージを表示
  - 商品画像は Shopify CDN で自動最適化(WebP 対応)
  - モバイルでは横スクロール、PC ではグリッド表示に切替
動作確認バージョン: Online Store 2.0
ライセンス: ALSEL Original
============================================================
{% endcomment %}

{%- assign section_label = section.settings.heading | default: '関連商品' | escape -%}

<section class="alsel-related-products" aria-label="{{ section_label }}">
  <div class="alsel-related-products__inner">
    {%- if section.settings.heading != blank -%}
      <h2 class="alsel-related-products__heading">{{ section.settings.heading }}</h2>
    {%- endif -%}
    {%- if section.settings.subheading != blank -%}
      <p class="alsel-related-products__sub">{{ section.settings.subheading }}</p>
    {%- endif -%}

    {%- assign target_collection = collections[section.settings.collection] -%}
    {%- if target_collection != blank and target_collection.products.size > 0 -%}
      <div class="alsel-related-products__scroller" role="list">
        {%- assign max_items = section.settings.product_limit -%}
        {%- assign shown = 0 -%}
        {%- for product in target_collection.products -%}
          {%- if shown >= max_items -%}{%- break -%}{%- endif -%}
          {%- if product.handle == nil -%}{%- continue -%}{%- endif -%}
          {%- if template contains 'product' and product.id == product.id and product.handle == product.handle -%}{%- endif -%}
          {%- assign alt_text = product.title | escape -%}
          <article class="alsel-related-products__card" role="listitem">
            <a class="alsel-related-products__link" href="{{ product.url }}" aria-label="{{ alt_text }}の詳細を見る">
              <div class="alsel-related-products__media">
                {%- if product.featured_image != blank -%}
                  {{ product.featured_image
                    | image_url: width: 600
                    | image_tag: loading: 'lazy', class: 'alsel-related-products__image', alt: alt_text, widths: '200, 400, 600, 800' }}
                {%- else -%}
                  <div class="alsel-related-products__image alsel-related-products__image--empty" aria-hidden="true">No Image</div>
                {%- endif -%}
                {%- if section.settings.show_soldout and product.available == false -%}
                  <span class="alsel-related-products__badge">SOLD OUT</span>
                {%- endif -%}
              </div>
              <div class="alsel-related-products__body">
                <h3 class="alsel-related-products__title">{{ product.title }}</h3>
                {%- if section.settings.show_price -%}
                  <p class="alsel-related-products__price">
                    {%- if product.compare_at_price > product.price -%}
                      <span class="alsel-related-products__price-sale">{{ product.price | money }}</span>
                      <span class="alsel-related-products__price-compare">{{ product.compare_at_price | money }}</span>
                    {%- else -%}
                      <span class="alsel-related-products__price-normal">{{ product.price | money }}</span>
                    {%- endif -%}
                  </p>
                {%- endif -%}
              </div>
            </a>
          </article>
          {%- assign shown = shown | plus: 1 -%}
        {%- endfor -%}
      </div>
    {%- else -%}
      <p class="alsel-related-products__empty">
        表示する商品はまだありません。テーマエディタからコレクションをご選択ください。
      </p>
    {%- endif -%}
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .alsel-related-products { padding: 3rem 1rem; background: {{ section.settings.bg_color }}; }
  .alsel-related-products__inner { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .alsel-related-products__heading { font-size: clamp(1.4rem, 4vw, 2rem); font-weight: 700; text-align: center; margin: 0 0 0.5rem; color: {{ section.settings.text_color }}; }
  .alsel-related-products__sub { font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.6; text-align: center; margin: 0 0 2rem; color: {{ section.settings.text_color }}; opacity: 0.75; }
  .alsel-related-products__empty { text-align: center; color: #888; padding: 2rem 0; font-size: 0.95rem; }
  .alsel-related-products__scroller {
    display: grid;
    grid-auto-flow: column;
    grid-auto-columns: 70%;
    gap: 1rem;
    overflow-x: auto;
    scroll-snap-type: x mandatory;
    -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
