{% comment %}
============================================================
セクション名: レビュー横スクロール
用途: お客様の口コミ・レビューを横スワイプで一覧表示し、購入の安心感を伝える
推奨設置場所: トップページ・商品ページ・LP の中盤(商品紹介の後など)
カスタマイズポイント:
  - セクション見出し・サブコピー
  - 背景色・カード色・星の色
  - 各レビューブロック(顧客名・属性・星評価・本文・画像)
  - ブロックの追加・削除でレビュー数を変更
注意点:
  - レビュー画像は任意(推奨 400 × 400px、JPEG または PNG)
  - スマホでは横スワイプ、PC では複数枚並べて表示する
  - ブロックは 3〜10 個推奨
動作確認バージョン: Online Store 2.0
ライセンス: ALSEL Original
============================================================
{% endcomment %}

<section class="alsel-review-carousel" aria-label="{{ section.settings.heading | escape | default: 'お客様のレビュー' }}">
  <div class="alsel-review-carousel__head">
    {%- if section.settings.heading != blank -%}
      <h2 class="alsel-review-carousel__heading">{{ section.settings.heading }}</h2>
    {%- endif -%}
    {%- if section.settings.subheading != blank -%}
      <p class="alsel-review-carousel__sub">{{ section.settings.subheading }}</p>
    {%- endif -%}
  </div>

  {%- if section.blocks.size > 0 -%}
    <div class="alsel-review-carousel__track" role="list">

  {%- if section.blocks.size == 0 -%}
    <p class="alsel-review-carousel__empty" style="text-align:center;color:#888;padding:2rem 0;">現在表示できるレビューはありません。テーマエディタからブロックを追加してください。</p>
  {%- endif -%}
    {%- for block in section.blocks -%}
        <article class="alsel-review-carousel__card" role="listitem" {{ block.shopify_attributes }}>
          {%- assign rating = block.settings.rating | times: 1 -%}
          <div class="alsel-review-carousel__stars" aria-label="星{{ rating }}つの評価">
            {%- for i in (1..5) -%}
              {%- if i <= rating -%}
                <span class="alsel-review-carousel__star alsel-review-carousel__star--on" aria-hidden="true">★</span>
              {%- else -%}
                <span class="alsel-review-carousel__star" aria-hidden="true">★</span>
              {%- endif -%}
            {%- endfor -%}
          </div>

          {%- if block.settings.title != blank -%}
            <h3 class="alsel-review-carousel__title">{{ block.settings.title | escape }}</h3>
          {%- endif -%}

          {%- if block.settings.body != blank -%}
            <p class="alsel-review-carousel__body">{{ block.settings.body | escape | newline_to_br }}</p>
          {%- endif -%}

          <div class="alsel-review-carousel__person">
            {%- if block.settings.avatar != blank -%}
              {%- assign alt_1 = block.settings.name | escape -%}
{{ block.settings.avatar | image_url: width: 120 | image_tag: loading: 'lazy', class: 'alsel-review-carousel__avatar', alt: alt_1, widths: '60, 120, 180' }}
            {%- endif -%}
            <div class="alsel-review-carousel__meta">
              {%- if block.settings.name != blank -%}
                <span class="alsel-review-carousel__name">{{ block.settings.name | escape }}</span>
              {%- endif -%}
              {%- if block.settings.attribute != blank -%}
                <span class="alsel-review-carousel__attr">{{ block.settings.attribute | escape }}</span>
              {%- endif -%}
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
      {%- endfor -%}
    </div>
  {%- endif -%}
</section>

<style>
  .alsel-review-carousel {
    --bg: {{ section.settings.bg_color }};
    --card-bg: {{ section.settings.card_color }};
    --text: {{ section.settings.text_color }};
    --star: {{ section.settings.star_color }};
    --accent: {{ section.settings.accent_color }};
    padding: 3rem 0;
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--text);
  }
  .alsel-review-carousel__head { text-align: center; padding: 0 1.5rem; margin: 0 0 2rem; }
  .alsel-review-carousel__heading { font-size: clamp(1.4rem, 4vw, 2.2rem); font-weight: 700; margin: 0 0 0.5rem; line-height: 1.4; }
  .alsel-review-carousel__sub { font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.7; opacity: 0.8; margin: 0; }
  .alsel-review-carousel__track {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    overflow-x: auto;
    scroll-snap-type: x mandatory;
    padding: 0.5rem 1.5rem 1.5rem;
    -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;
    scrollbar-width: thin;
  }
  .alsel-review-carousel__track::-webkit-scrollbar { height: 6px; }
  .alsel-review-carousel__track::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: var(--accent); border-radius: 9999px; }
  .alsel-review-carousel__card {
    flex: 0 0 80%;
    max-width: 320px;
    scroll-snap-align: start;
    background: var(--card-bg);
    border-radius: 14px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 14px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }
  .alsel-review-carousel__stars { display: flex; gap: 2px; font-size: 1.1rem; letter-spacing: 1px; }
  .alsel-review-carousel__star { color: #e5e7eb; }
  .alsel-review-carousel__star--on { color: var(--star); }
  .alsel-review-carousel__title { font-size: 1.05rem; font-weight: 700; margin: 0; line-height: 1.5; }
  .alsel-review-carousel__body { font-size: 0.92rem; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0; flex: 1; }
  .alsel-review-carousel__person { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.75rem; padding-top: 0.75rem; border-top: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.08); }
  .alsel-review-carousel__avatar { width: 44px; height: 44px; border-radius: 50%; object-fit: cover; }
  .alsel-review-carousel__meta { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 2px; }
  .alsel-review-carousel__name { font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 700; }
  .alsel-review-carousel__attr { font-size: 0.8rem; opacity: 0.7; }
  @media (min-width: 750px) {
    .alsel-review-carousel { padding: 5rem 0; }
    .alsel-review-carousel__track { gap: 1.5rem; padding: 0.5rem 2.5rem 2rem; max-width: 1280px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .alsel-review-carousel__card { flex: 0 0 calc((100% - 3rem) / 3); max-width: none; padding: 2rem; }
  }
</style>

